{
  "stem": "13219.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Americans came-- at that time, maybe they came from Italy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came from-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- it could be maybe the later part because it was chilly at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a few weeks in Pilzno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember going to a steam bath to Prague.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never saw a steam bath like this in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With lice?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Plenty of lice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't help ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What you used to do, you used to take the shirt and turn over on the other side and just go throw on the fire to burn them off.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the eggs were still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and we came-- finally, we came to our destination that's where-- which I stayed in, in Linz, by the name of Bindermichl--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bindermichl.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--which used to be-- used to be the barracks-- not the barracks, the homes for the Germans, German officers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The families used to live there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's where they, they took, and they made a DP camp for the people in Linz-Bindermichl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Austria.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, we felt like we owned the city because with-- there was nothing to afraid already there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we used to run around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they, they were like the beaten people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They weren't too demanding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wherever we went, nobody touched us at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very nicely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a few friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were a gang of-- gang about eight people, 10 people, which we used to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means take revenge whatever we could because the Austrians were worse than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About this?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to-- first of all we bought an old car, all of us, by making a few bucks in the camp by selling cigarettes-- American cigarettes--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is still during the war?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
